==English==

===Etymology===

From [[Latin]] ''-acea'': neutral plural of ''[[-aceus]]'' - belonging to, the nature of (enlarged from adjective suffix ''[[-ax]]'', genitive of ''[[-acis]]'').

===Suffix===
'''-acea'''
# [[taxonomic]] [[superfamily]] of [[plant]]s, [[algae]] and [[fungi]]

===Derived terms===
*very many

